```plantuml
@startuml gaiax_fLibra
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor User

rectangle "Frontend (Nuxt.js)" as FE {
}

rectangle "Libra Blockchain" as LibraChain #mistyrose

rectangle "Ethereum Blockchain" as EthereumChain #lightyellow {
  rectangle "Smart Contracts\n(Flibra.sol, ItemDetail.sol)" as SmartContracts #palegreen
}

rectangle "Firestore" as Firestore #aliceblue

rectangle "IPFS" as IPFS #lightblue

rectangle "Elasticsearch Service" as Elasticsearch #lightsteelblue

' ========== Connections ==========
User --> FE

' Frontend interactions
FE <--> LibraChain : interact with Libra wallet\nfor transactions
FE <--> EthereumChain : interact with\nsmart contracts
FE <--> Firestore : fetch/store user/item data\nfetch/store reviews
FE <--> IPFS : upload/download item and\nprofile images

' Firestore interactions
Firestore --> Elasticsearch : onSnapshot listeners\nupdate index

' Elasticsearch interactions
Elasticsearch --> Firestore : register new items\nremove sold items

@enduml
```